--- Join single condition ---
Output: a, b, x, y

Join (JOIN FillRightFirst)
│  t1 ⋈ t2
│  Type: inner | Strictness: all | Algorithm: ConcurrentHashJoin
│  Join conditions: a = x
│  Output:
│    Left:  a, b
│    Right: x, y
├──ReadFromMergeTree (default.t1)
│     Read type: Default
│     Parts: 1 | Granules: 1
│     Output: a, b
└──ReadFromMergeTree (default.t2)
      Read type: Default
      Parts: 1 | Granules: 1
      Output: x, y
--- Join null-safe ---
Output: a, b, x, y

Join (JOIN FillRightFirst)
│  t1 ⋈ t2
│  Type: inner | Strictness: all | Algorithm: ConcurrentHashJoin
│  Join conditions: a <=> x
│  Output:
│    Left:  a, b
│    Right: x, y
├──ReadFromMergeTree (default.t1)
│     Read type: Default
│     Parts: 1 | Granules: 1
│     Output: a, b
└──ReadFromMergeTree (default.t2)
      Read type: Default
      Parts: 1 | Granules: 1
      Output: x, y
