--- Multi-key IN ---
Output: a, b

Filter ((WHERE + Change column names to column identifiers))
│  Filter column: tuple(a, b) IN ((1, \'x\'), (2, \'y\'))
└──ReadFromMergeTree (default.t1)
      Read type: Default
      Parts: 1 | Granules: 1
      Output: a, b
